&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are an award-winning independent creative solutions company that aspires to be the most culturally-influential company in the world. We help ambitious brands harness the power of culture to solve their biggest challenges. As a unique mix of experts in culture, technology, and storytelling, we are united by a passion to grow brands in ways that advertising alone can never do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are an entrepreneurial business — not a traditional &quot;ad agency.&quot; That means we value resourcefulness and tenacity just as much as we value creativity and intelligence. We&#39;re unapologetically ambitious.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for talented Strategists to join Translation+.&lt;/p&gt;
