&lt;li&gt;Experience in building relationships with account, creative, legal, production, &amp;amp; finance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to meet deadlines with accuracy and minimum supervision&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills and high attention to detail&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
