&lt;li&gt;Define and articulate a multi-platform UX strategy spanning iOS, Android, and web.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish a unified design language and systems that scale across mobile and desktop experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion simplicity, accessibility, and consistency across all surfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
