&lt;li&gt;Lead critical product surfaces including onboarding, distribution tools, subscription areas, analytics, payments, and artist monetization features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate directly with engineers to ensure designs are technically feasible and implemented with high fidelity across platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach designers on mobile UI patterns, responsive design, gesture-based interaction, and layout systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
